data.description: Ask about INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN options for this property. Gorgeous three bedroom room two full bath sanctuary! Split Floor Plan, 42" Beechwood Custom Cabinets Spacious rooms, office/study that could be used as a 4th bedroom, walk in pantry, spacious laundry room in close proximity to the primary bedroom and walk in closet for easy access, office nook just off from the garage entrance, two car attached garage with built in storage shelves. Well manicured landscaping and natural stones adorning your main entrance. Bonus room for entertainment!  A must see and you do not want to miss out on this rare find! Interstate about 5-7 minutes away and all of the finer things Hammond has to offer is within a desirable distance. Easy to show. Same day showings allowed.
